doctype html
html
  head
    meta(charset="utf-8")
    title Password Reset Request
  body
    h2 Hello #{name},
    p Someone (hopefully you) has requested a password reset for your Interact account.
    p If this was you, please click the button below to reset your password. The link is valid for 1 hour.
    a(href=url, target="_blank")
      button(style="padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #8B5CF6; color: white; border: none; border-radius: 5px; cursor: pointer;") Reset Password
    p If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email.
    p Thanks,
    p The Interact Team 